Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: It is worth a try. Very high quality in a cozy atmosphere. The Staff is very nice a friendly. They say you can find here the best chicken satay in town. It is true! Cakes are good too. Price/quality ratio is commensurate. Recommended for breakfast/lunch and dinner

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Love this place for breakfast, lunch, dinner, drinks and the-last-one-of-the-evening-drinks. The food is amazing for the price (actually just amazing, period), always fresh and plentiful (and I'm a big eater). Good selection of beers and …

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: A good find. Great atmosphere, good drinks and food. Nice spot to eat and talk. They also have games for those wanting to play and spend time.

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Delicious burger and fries. We went on Wednesday: Burger Night, burger and fries for €10! The ginger beer is good too!

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Pretty good experience! The staff is very friendly, they have a good wine selection and the space is very good looking!

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Amazing, unique tasting food! Burger was the most flavorful burger I've ever had. My friend had the mixed grill- highly recommended as well! Decently priced. Super sweet waiter/manager Tijs! (He makes an amazing Amaretto Sour). Would …

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Great place for a dinner! Nice and cozy. There are cool games as well. The only con is that, for the size of the dishes, it's a bit pricey.

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Lovely bar. The small menu is tasty and well presented. The owner is truly welcoming and attentive! And above all reasonable pricing. 5 stars!

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Good beer, good food, great service!

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: A pearl in Amsterdam Oost! The waiter (owner?) was attentive and nice, cozy and unique environment, amazing food. We ordered a BLT and a Burratasandwich, both og which tasted great. Big portions, great value for the money.

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Really nice atmosphere, the best little  pancakes with chocolate and vanilla ice and fruit ever!!!! Late in the evening, big screen with sport, beautiful location.

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Nice small restaurant with friendly staff. We had the fish & chips and the wisse burger. Both were super and I will definitely return!

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Small but delicious menu, fresh products, good vibes in the evening. :)

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text:
Food is ok, nothing mind-blowing, but the main thing for me here is: Pilsener Urquell on tap!
One of the few places in the region that offers this top-notch Czech beer!

Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: Small cozy bar / restaurant! Great to hava a coffee in the afternoon with the sun or a nice dinner with friends, they serve very good finger  food.
